    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis.<persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/32"> Karolus </persName>divina
                        favente clementia<rs key="#Emperor/king"> imperator </rs>augustus. Si
                        petitionibus fidelium nostrorum maxime eorum, qui nostro fideliter parent
                        imperio, aures celsitudinis nostre accomodamus, non solum imperialem in hoc
                        exercemus dignitatem, verum etiam eterne retributionis premia inde nobis
                        largiri procul dubio credimus. Quapropter cognoscat omnium fidelium
                        nostrorum presentium videlicet et futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/33"
                            >Liutuuardum </persName>venerabilem <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs> et
                        dilectum <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicanzellarium</rs> nostram postulasse
                        serenitatem, ut sanctissimo <orgName>patri Eusebio</orgName> defensori
                        christiane fidei aliqua de iure regni nostri concederemus et aliqua que
                        subtracta sunt redderemus. Statimque nos postulationes illius saluberrimas
                        agnoscentes decrevimus ita fieri. Concessimus itaque prefato sancto Eusebio
                        cortem nostram magnam que dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Fiscal_property #Object #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/60">Regio </geogName>antiquo
                        nuncupatur vulgo cum tota<rs key="#Forests"> silva </rs>eiusdem et
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/49">fulgitio</placeName>
                        et cum omnibus cortibus et villis, cum <placeName>valle Cliui</placeName> et
                        omnibus eorum pertinentiis simul cum corte de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            >Roueredo</geogName> cum omnibus suis adiacentiis, dedimus etiam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            >cortem</rs> nostram magnam que dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/62"><placeName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/50" key="#Curtes">Bugella
                            </placeName></geogName>cum omnibus cortibus et villis alpibus et omnibus
                        suis pertinentiis, contulimus et reddidimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/63"><placeName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/51"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Profits_of_justice #Tolls #Teloneum"
                                >Sestinium</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus alpibus et
                        pertinentiis suis, ut muris sanctis in censuali calce perpetuo deserviret,
                        donavimus et restituimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object">Romanianum</geogName> cum omnibus
                        suis vallibus alpibus et suis pertinentiis, et confirmavimus totam <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvam </rs><placeName key="#Forests"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/96">Rouasindam
                        </placeName>pertinentem ad <rs key="#Plebs">plebem </rs>sancti Laurentii
                        ipsius Vercellensis ecclesie, reddidimus et confirmavimus<rs
                            key="#Bridges/pontoons"> pontem </rs>Notingum, quem Notingus episcopus
                        eiusdem Vercellensis ecclesie mirabiliter super eum equitando per legem
                        recepit, dedimus cortem <geogName key="#Curtes">Trecade </geogName>cum
                        omnibus suis pertinentiis, dedimus <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/96">cortem iuris nostri <placeName
                                key="#Curtes" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/99"
                                >Firminianam</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis,
                        obtulimus et restituimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/41">Carixianam </geogName>cum
                            <placeName key="#Curtes">Langusco</placeName> sibi adiacente et cum
                        omnibus suis pertinentiis, largiti sumus et reddidimus cortes de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object">Pasiliano</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object">Occimiano</geogName> cum omnibus
                        suis pertinentiis. Hec omnia sancta Vercellensis ecclesia proprio iure in
                        eternum habeat cum omnibus publicis <rs key="#Profits_of_justice"
                            >districtis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Periodic_markets">mercatis </rs><rs key="#Teloneum">toloneis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">piscationibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus</rs> portibus
                        molendinis montibus et vallibus alpibus edificiis <rs key="#Slave"
                            >mancipiis</rs> utriusque sexus agris vineis capellis pratis pascuis
                        silvis <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis aquarumque
                        </rs>decursibus cultis et incultis et de nostro iure et dominio in ius et
                        dominium prelibate ecclesie tradimus atque transfundimus. Si quis autem hanc
                        nostram traditionem infringere temptaverit, eiusdem piissimi Eusebii iram
                        incurrat, insuper rectoribus ecclesie persolvendum centum libras auri
                        purissimi culpabilis habeatur. Et ut hec traditio pleniorem in dei nomine
                        obtineat firmitatem, hoc nostre auctoritatis preceptum fieri mandavimus
                        propriaque manu confirmantes anulo nostro iussimus sigillari. Signum (M.)
                        domni Karoli serenissimi imperatoris augusti. </ab>
                </div>
